    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="container reveal">
        <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="glass-panel about-glass">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-brain"></i> Passion & Mindset</h3>
                <p>I am driven by a deep-seated passion for cyber defense, specifically inside the modern Security Operations Center (SOC) framework. My problem-solving methodology combines critical analysis and threat intelligence, allowing me to map alerts to attacker tactics and implement rapid containment procedures.</p>
                <p>Always pushing to stay ahead of the threats, I focus on automating detection workflows, parsing complex log formats, and aligning defense strategies with global framework benchmarks.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-panel about-glass">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> SOC Journey & Goals</h3>
                <p>Through comprehensive hands-on internships, I have built real-world competence in SIEM dashboard configuration, deep packet analysis using Wireshark, active directory testing, and auditing. I work to cultivate a rigorous security posture daily.</p>
                <p>My career roadmap is laser-focused on becoming a key asset to tier-1 blue teams, where I can proactively hunt threats, protect valuable organizational assets, and drive business compliance.</p>
            </div>
